00:12:27.520 --> 00:12:28.920
na may malinaw na background.

00:12:29.760 --> 00:12:31.040
Gayunpaman, aking Panginoon,

00:12:31.720 --> 00:12:32.880
bilang isang medikal na opisyal,

00:12:33.080 --> 00:12:33.920
Maaari kang gumawa ng martial arts,

00:12:34.440 --> 00:12:35.440
at ang iyong mga kasanayang medikal

00:12:35.800 --> 00:12:37.040
hindi pa rin malinaw.

00:12:38.040 --> 00:12:39.760
Ang dahilan kung bakit ka pumasok
sa Imperial Medical Bureau

00:12:40.200 --> 00:12:41.520
palaisipan talaga sa akin.

00:12:45.560 --> 00:12:46.400
Attendant Rong, narito

00:12:46.880 --> 00:12:47.720
isang piraso ng payo.

00:12:48.280 --> 00:12:49.360
Masyadong curiosity

00:12:50.000 --> 00:12:51.240
baka malagay ka sa gulo.

00:12:52.720 --> 00:12:53.880
Isa lang ang kailangan mong malaman.

00:12:54.480 --> 00:12:55.840
I mean walang masama sa bureau.

00:12:57.080 --> 00:12:58.120
Oo, Panginoon ko.

00:13:04.480 --> 00:13:05.320
Attendant Rong,

00:13:06.240 --> 00:13:07.240
I can sense

00:13:07.720 --> 00:13:09.320
isang mapanganib na aura sa iyo.

00:13:10.520 --> 00:13:11.960
mas maganda ka

00:13:12.320 --> 00:13:13.240
itago mong mabuti ang iyong sarili.

00:13:13.680 --> 00:13:15.040
Kung mahuli kita isang araw,

00:13:15.520 --> 00:13:17.480
malalagay sa panganib ang iyong buhay.

00:13:18.800 --> 00:13:19.880
Parehong payo para sa iyo.

00:13:20.560 --> 00:13:23.400
Kung tutuusin, hindi naman ako
maamo na tupa na naghihintay na katayin.

00:13:24.600 --> 00:13:25.440
Iyan ay magandang malaman.

